me":"2019-02-27T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"咁如果第二個宇宙數字嘅定義都變埋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:16:33.000Z","msg":"例如第二個宇宙 佢地數字順序係<br />\n1 3 2 4 5... 咁樣1+1=3 但意思上都係講緊一個object +一個object 出 兩個object"},{"pid":"fa414e2982d36d600dc5b04704d40b287309adfe","tid":1038381,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:21:18.000Z","msg":"你個物理嘅定義咁寬，咁有乜嘢可以脫離物理?"},{"pid":"e14d83a87d5bd0e91bf7629865d8e95d498c04c7","tid":1038381,"uid":67779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"倒轉講先啱喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單到連海王星都係靠數學推測出嚟發現，而唔係物理觀察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371762e80741de705ad14003a3cd8178b5428df7","tid":1038381,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"文學無法脫離文字"},{"pid":"d32a17fba11656549203a0e60e3e5b303b906ee4","tid":1038381,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79b91175cfa607f1a7d24a16633c66dabce615b9","tid":1038381,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40e920de580b9f2702b9f28934bc7e8763ef2594","tid":1038381,"uid":165159,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:45:53.000Z","msg":"數學係任何宇宙都work<br />\n物理係唔同宇宙會唔work<br />\n例如 萬有引力,F=ma 呢啲 我地只係發現有呢種法則<br />\n但解釋唔到既 係第二個宇宙就有機會唔同咗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"第二個宇宙會唔會有1+1=3嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"量子世界已經係咁，1+1 根本唔知等於乜"},{"pid":"83534f654e0b75968bd06e8647df5c1cc3091ea7","tid":1038381,"uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"數學根本就係等於物理，兩者同時存在，同一樣野。<br />\n<br />\n只不過我哋由人類研究者嘅角度去睇， 有時只係見到數學嘅一面唔了解呢個數學背後演繹嘅物理性質，或者調返轉我哋發現左物理性質之後再搵返佢背後嘅數學語言。<br />\n<br />\n情況就好似一幅雙面砌圖咁，前後都有圖像，一面叫數學一面叫物理， 但其實佢哋係同一幅砌圖，每一塊都有兩面。"},{"pid":"bbc51f95c5590a4b2e97403c6cb5337779920279","tid":1038381,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"我想知你點知完美嘅圓(或其概念)係存在於腦神經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係咪知道人腦某種pattern嘅電波/排列就等於完美嘅圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪個個人嘅pattern都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相關研究係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果外星人/人工智能明咩係完美嘅圓，咁佢地嘅&quot;腦&quot;係咪會出現同人類一樣嘅pattern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之就係，你點確定到同一個概念係腦入面有同樣嘅物理表現/形態？如果同一個概念冇同一樣嘅物理表現/形態，咁邊個形態先係你口中所講嘅某概念嘅實體？"},{"pid":"b14d117d591df641dfef1c998c623dab37c78ea6","tid":1038381,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fb3ee9c62e4705e67315c90f562f4d41e78afcd","tid":1038381,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddec9af23fdda2e4e4075ec25cb4ca075a83f271","tid":1038381,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1219e7071c7a57b0163f229cef7aec118eae62be","tid":1038381,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"Perfect circle exist in virtual world, But virtual worlds base on physical world<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完美圓以概念方式存在，概念存在於人類大腦神經，腦神經架設於物理世界，完美圓於物理世界以特殊方式存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"圓點「存在」喺神經？你指嚟睇下。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:12:50.000Z","msg":"咁都唔明就躝翻去波台啦，講完又要人講多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"世上冇「特殊存在」，只有存在。<br />\n存在嘅嘢，除咗光之外都有質量，而且佔有空間，一個圓點樣喺腦裏面佔有空間？點樣有質量？你解釋唔到，就咁話咩「特殊存在」只係想偷換概念。"}]}